summary: Live in a Castle!!! Currently taking suggestions for new content.  Requires Dawnguard.  Best to have all other DLC to be sure, and the latest update.
descriptionHtml:
Live in this Castle!!! This is my first mod, I dont expect it to get many downloads since its kinda late for mods. I am taking suggestions so feel free to comment. I will try my best to add what you guys want into the castle. To get the Lingerie that the slaves are wearing you need these two mods:
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28714/?
I would personally like to thank Caliente for all of the great mods they've made.
I would also like to thank Nausicaa for the outfits.
Please don't hesitate to comment.
The entrance is in the pool of water on the right while going up the stairs to Dragonsreach.
author: Ghostunit119
